  m_Name: Q_5_2
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Question
  questionID: question4.2
  questionText: "Heating 12g of limestone (CaCO3\u200B) produces a solid mixture
    weighing 8.4g. The mass of CO2\u200B gas released is: "
  answers:
  - 3.6
  - 1.8
  - 2.4
  - 6.4
  correctIndex: 0
  explanation: "Mass of limestone=Mass of remaining solid+Mass of released CO2\u200B
    Mass of CO2\u200B=12\u22128.4=3.6 (grams)"
